GoogleMapControl v7

GoogleMapControl v7.0 is out now - it is a commercial version with 30 days trial period.
You can find more info about the new control and all the new GoogleMaps API v3 features it supports now at:
  • Website http://googlemapcontrol.com/
  • Nuget https://www.nuget.org/packages/GoogleMapControl
  • Samples http://googlemapcontrol.com/
  • Documentation http://codesamples.googlemapcontrol.com/
